Psychologist must pay for tx fees.

div.div: The psychologist confirms that they joined the chat. If the pyschologist joined the chat on time, the state of the session box changes to confirm this. If the psychologist is greater than 5 minutes late than the client gets a 10% discount, if the psychologist is greater than 10 minutes late then the client gets a 50% discount. This information can be stored in the registers of the sessions box.
